ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.v23.message

Class ADT_A14

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.AbstractStructure
      • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.AbstractGroup
        • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.AbstractMessage
          • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.v23.message.ADT_A14
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Group, Message, Structure, Visitable, Serializable

    public class ADT_A14
extends AbstractMessage

    Represents a ADT_A14 message structure (see chapter ?). This structure contains the following elements:

    • 1: MSH (Message header segment)
    • 2: EVN (Event type)
    • 3: PID (Patient Identification)
    • 4: PD1 (Patient Demographic) optional
    • 5: NK1 (Next of kin) optional repeating
    • 6: PV1 (Patient visit)
    • 7: PV2 (Patient visit - additional information) optional
    • 8: DB1 (Disability Segment) optional repeating
    • 9: OBX (Observation segment) optional repeating
    • 10: AL1 (Patient allergy information) optional repeating
    • 11: DG1 (Diagnosis) optional repeating
    • 12: DRG (Diagnosis Related Group) optional
    • 13: ADT_A14_PROCEDURE (a Group object) optional repeating
    • 14: GT1 (Guarantor) optional repeating
    • 15: ADT_A14_INSURANCE (a Group object) optional repeating
    • 16: ACC (Accident) optional
    • 17: UB1 (UB82 data) optional
    • 18: UB2 (UB92 data) optional
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
